headline: How successful was Tesla's robotaxi launch?
summary: Tesla (TSLA) stock is trading higher after the electric vehicle (EV) pioneer's robotaxi launch event in Austin on Sunday. Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi and Yahoo Finance anchor Julie Hyman chat with Washington Crossing Advisors senior portfolio manager Chad Morganlander and Innovator ETFs chief investment strategist Tim Urbanowicz about the event and what it means for Tesla investors.
